Package: sqlr
Title: Build SQL queries for creating/altering tables
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Nicolas", "Bennett", email = "nicolas.bennett@stat.math.ethz.ch",
           role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description:
    Starting with MarinaDB/MySQL and possibly expanding to other SQL dialects, the aim of this package is to help with generating queries for creating and altering tables.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.0)
Imports:
    DBI (>= 0.7),
    RMariaDB (>= 1.0),
    blob,
    bit64,
    hms,
    rlang,
    tibble,
    yaml,
    methods
Suggests:
    testthat
URL: https://github.com/nbenn/sqlr
BugReports: https://github.com/nbenn/sqlr/issues
